Title: Authorizes the assessor of Nassau county to accept an application for retroactive real property tax exempt status from Al-Muneer Foundation, Inc.
Summary: Authorizes the assessor of Nassau county to accept an application for retroactive real property tax exempt status from Al-Muneer Foundation, Inc.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to authorizing the county of Nassau assessor to accept an application for a real property tax exemption from Al-Muneer Foundation, Inc.
